{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"6ec5959dc6","title":"对北约空军演习情况报告的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"9542a09393","index":0,"year":1955,"month":10,"day":19,"articleId":"6ec5959dc6"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji35","name":"毛泽东全集第35卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/35-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji35":{"comments":[{"id":"1ac364c730","publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"6ec5959dc6","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这是毛泽东对中共中央军委委员、国务院副总理兼国防部部长彭德怀1955年10月13日报告的批语。"},{"id":"dde252b527","publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"6ec5959dc6","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指彭德怀转呈的由中国驻德意志民主共和国大使馆研究室编写的专题资料。资料介绍了北大西洋公约组织1955年6月底在西德、荷兰、比利时和法国东部举行的代号为“空白纸”的空军演习情况。此次演习，美、英等国空军出动飞机3000多架，历时8天，是第二次世界大战后最大规模的空军演习，其目的在于试验“闪击式原子战”的可能性和效果。对演习结果有不同反映，美英方面偏重于夸大原子弹威力和强调主动进攻的优越性，某些高级军官公开表示未来的世界大战可在几天内决定胜负，西德国防部部长则强调建立陆军的必要性。"}],"contents":[{"id":"55c0d821d2","type":"title","text":"对北约空军演习情况报告的批语则","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"6ec5959dc6"},{"id":"1ac364c730","type":"paragraph","text":"此件可以一阅。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"6ec5959dc6"},{"id":"dde252b527","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"6ec5959dc6"},{"id":"c3ae248be7","type":"paragraph","text":"十月十九日","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"6ec5959dc6"}],"page":{"id":"6090fa34df","publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"6ec5959dc6","start":523,"end":523}}}},"__N_SSG":true}